<#----------------------------------
    .SYNOPSIS  
        Create multiple dummy log files.
    .NOTES 
	   Created to test some .zip functionality. Creates multiple files and hopefully differnet directories
    .AUTHOR
        Author
    .LOGIC
        For loop created to create files with name format of "File_00 {incrementing number}".log. Creates as many as you need, using the textvalue field. The usual file size is 12KB.
    .FUNCTIONS
	   Functions written into code
    .VERSION
        1.0
    .EXAMPLE USAGE
	   Run this from either ISE, VS Code, or just as a regular .ps1 file
----------------------------------#>

